PART B Programs

1.	Write a program to demonstrate ordered list and its tags <ol> and <li>
<html>
<head>
<title>Ordered list</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="red">
<h4>list of fruits</h4>
<ol type="A" start="A">
<li>Strawberry</li>
<li>Fig</li>
<li>Mango</li>
<li>Pineapple</li>
</ol>
<h4>List of Vegetables</h4>
<ol type="i" start="i">
<li>tomato</li>
<li>cauliflower</li>
<li>carrot</li>
<li>beans</li>
</ol>
<h4>list of cereals</h4>
<ol type="1" start="1">
<li>rice</li>
<li>jowar</li>
<li>groundnuts</li>
</ol>
</body>
</html>

